comments: Omoruyi (OKC) and Reid (MIN) engage and disengage with one another and marginal contact occurs as the screen is set.
Edwards (MIN) brushes Giddey's (OKC) arm and marginal contact occurs during his driving shot attempt.
Reid (MIN) slides his pivot foot at the start of his dribble.
Nowell (MIN) legally contests Gilgeous-Alexander's (OKC) jump shot attempt.
Gilgeous-Alexander (OKC) contests the jump shot attempt and marginal contact occurs with Edwards' (MIN) arm after the release.
Anderson (MIN) delivers body contact to Williams (OKC) that affects his SQBR during the drive.
Reid (MIN) is in the paint for longer than three seconds without imminently actively guarding an opponent.
Rivers (MIN) is moving alongside Gilgeous-Alexander's (OKC) path and marginal body contact occurs as they come together during the drive.
Gilgeous-Alexander (OKC) steps through and marginal contact occurs with Rivers (MIN) as he naturally clears space.
Edwards (MIN) contests and makes clean contact with the ball during Gilgeous-Alexander's (OKC) shot attempt near the rim.
Omoruyi (OKC) establishes himself in Edwards' (MIN) path and does not deliver illegal contact.
Reid (MIN) delivers body contact to Gilgeous-Alexander (OKC) that affects his SQBR during the drive.
Wiggins (OKC) initiates contact with Edwards' (MIN) arm that affects his SQBR.
Anderson (MIN) does not leave the designated throw-in space.
Omoruyi (OKC) initiates arm contact with Reid (MIN) that affects his SQBR.
Rivers (MIN) initiates contact with Gilgeous-Alexander's (OKC) arm that affects his SQBR prior to his upward shooting motion.
Gilgeous-Alexander (OKC) crosses the plane of the free throw line before his FTA makes contact with the rim.
Wiggins (OKC) initiates contact with Edwards' (MIN) arm during the drive that affects his SQBR.
